query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mi_idx it) NoMergeJoin(it mi_idx mk) NoHashJoin(it mi_idx mk k) NoMergeJoin(it k mi_idx mk t) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND mi_idx.info > '11' AND it.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword like '%sequel%'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2004;
